Package: umap3dGIF
Type: Package
Title: Create 3D UMAP Rotating GIF Animations from Seurat Objects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ayumu", "Okumura", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate rotating 3D UMAP visualizations as GIF animations from
    Seurat single-cell RNA-seq objects.  Supports custom coloring, cluster labeling,
    and memory-optimized frame generation.
